### Ping Controller Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiVersion = v1

### 1. Simple Ping - Debe retornar "pong"
#@no-cookie-jar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/ping
Accept: application/json

### 2. Ping con mensaje personalizado
#@no-cookie-jar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/ping/hello
Accept: application/json

### 3. Health Check
#@no-cookie-jar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/ping/health
Accept: application/json

### 4. Ping con mensaje largo
#@no-cookie-jar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/ping/this-is-a-long-message
Accept: application/json

### 5. Ping con caracteres especiales
#@no-cookie-jar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/ping/hello-world-2024
Accept: application/json

